Nell Tiger Free https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nell_Tiger_Free 0 Nell Tiger Free is an English actress and singer best known for her role as Myrcella Baratheon in seasons 5 and 6 of the television series Game of Thrones, where she replaced Aimee Richardson. She is also known for roles as Chloe Crumb in the film version of Mr. Stink and Anna in the film Broken.
